Fun project Slot Machine using Sencha Touch

Instructions:
Either:
Download the repository and open index.html in your web browser (Chrome, Safari, IE)

Or:
Put the Repository on a application server(WAMP/MAMP/XAMPP), and open the server location in iPhone/Android/Windows Phone 7

Enjoy playing Slot Machine.

Please have a look at this fiddle:

http://jsfiddle.net/hrishikeshp19/4rjFs/

The actual speed of slot machine hosted on a server is much better than what you can see in this fiddle. These speed limitations are because of jsfiddle.